@model CommunityCar.Mvc.ViewModels.Qa.QuestionsListViewModel
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IViewLocalizer Localizer
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = Localizer["My Questions"];
}

@section Styles {
    }

@{
    ViewData["HeaderTitle"] = Localizer["My Questions"];
    ViewData["HeaderDescription"] = Localizer["Manage your questions and track answers"];
    ViewData["HeaderIcon"] = "fas fa-user-circle";
    var createUrl = Url.Action("Create");
    var indexUrl = Url.Action("Index");
    var actionsHtml = "<div class='d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap'>" +
                      "<a href='" + createUrl + "' class='btn btn-light'>" +
                      "<i class='fas fa-plus-circle me-2'></i>" + Localizer["Ask Question"].Value +
                      "</a>" +
                      "<a href='" + indexUrl + "' class='btn btn-outline-light'>" +
                      "<i class='fas fa-arrow-left me-2'></i>" + Localizer["All Questions"].Value +
                      "</a>" +
                      "</div>";
    ViewData["HeaderActions"] = Html.Raw(actionsHtml);
}

<partial name="_InnerPageHeader" />

<!-- Alert Messages -->
@if (TempData["Success"] != null)
{
    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show rounded-4 shadow-sm" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>
        @TempData["Success"]
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
    </div>
}

@if (TempData["Error"] != null)
{
    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show rounded-4 shadow-sm" role="alert">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle me-2"></i>
        @TempData["Error"]
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
    </div>
}

<!-- Questions List -->
@if (!Model.Questions.Any())
{
    <div class="empty-state">
        <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i>
        <h3 class="mt-3 mb-2 fw-bold">@Localizer["No Questions Yet"]</h3>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4 fs-5">@Localizer["You haven't asked any questions. Start by asking your first question!"]</p>
        <a asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-gradient btn-lg">
            <i class="fas fa-plus-circle me-2"></i>@Localizer["Ask Your First Question"]
        </a>
    </div>
}
else
{
    <!-- Stats Summary -->
    <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <div class="text-primary mb-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-question-circle fa-2x"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-0 fw-bold">@Model.TotalCount</h3>
                    <small class="text-muted">@Localizer["Total Questions"]</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <div class="text-success mb-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle fa-2x"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-0 fw-bold">@Model.Questions.Count(q => q.IsResolved)</h3>
                    <small class="text-muted">@Localizer["Resolved"]</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <div class="text-warning mb-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock fa-2x"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-0 fw-bold">@Model.Questions.Count(q => !q.IsResolved)</h3>
                    <small class="text-muted">@Localizer["Open"]</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <div class="text-info mb-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-comments fa-2x"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="mb-0 fw-bold">@Model.Questions.Sum(q => q.AnswerCount)</h3>
                    <small class="text-muted">@Localizer["Total Answers"]</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-3">
        @foreach (var question in Model.Questions)
        {
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card question-card">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-auto">
                                <div class="stats-box">
                                    <div class="stat-item">
                                        <span class="stat-value">@question.VoteCount</span>
                                        <span class="stat-label">Votes</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <hr class="my-2">
                                    <div class="stat-item">
                                        <span class="stat-value @(question.IsResolved ? "resolved" : "")">@question.AnswerCount</span>
                                        <span class="stat-label">Answers</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <hr class="my-2">
                                    <div class="stat-item">
                                        <span class="stat-value">@question.ViewCount</span>
                                        <span class="stat-label">Views</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col">
                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start mb-2">
                                    <h5 class="card-title mb-0 flex-grow-1">
                                        <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-slug="@question.Slug" class="text-decoration-none text-dark fw-bold">
                                            @question.Title
                                        </a>
                                    </h5>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-2 align-items-center">
                                        @if (question.IsResolved)
                                        {
                                            <span class="badge bg-success rounded-pill px-3 py-2">
                                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i>Resolved
                                            </span>
                                        }
                                        else
                                        {
                                            <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark rounded-pill px-3 py-2">
                                                <i class="fas fa-clock me-1"></i>Open
                                            </span>
                                        }
                                        <div class="dropdown action-dropdown">
                                            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary rounded-circle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                                <i class="fas fa-ellipsis-v"></i>
                                            </button>
                                            <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end">
                                                <li>
                                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-action="Details" asp-route-slug="@question.Slug">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-eye me-2 text-primary"></i>View Details
                                                    </a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@question.Id">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-edit me-2 text-info"></i>Edit Question
                                                    </a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <button class="dropdown-item text-danger" onclick="deleteQuestion('@question.Id', '@question.Title')">
                                                        <i class="fas fa-trash me-2"></i>Delete Question
                                                    </button>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <p class="card-text text-muted mb-3">
                                    @(question.Content.Length > 250 ? question.Content.Substring(0, 250) + "..." : question.Content)
                                </p>

                                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(question.Tags))
                                {
                                    <div class="mb-3">
                                        @foreach (var tag in question.Tags.Split(',', StringSplitOptions.RemoveEmptyEntries).Take(5))
                                        {
                                            <a asp-action="Index" asp-route-tag="@tag.Trim()" class="tag-badge me-1 mb-1">
                                                <i class="fas fa-tag me-1"></i>@tag.Trim()
                                            </a>
                                        }
                                    </div>
                                }

                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
                                    <div class="text-muted small">
                                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-1"></i>
                                        Asked @question.CreatedAt.ToTimeAgo()
                                        @if (question.UpdatedAt.HasValue)
                                        {
                                            <span class="ms-2">
                                                <i class="fas fa-edit me-1"></i>
                                                Updated @question.UpdatedAt.Value.ToTimeAgo()
                                            </span>
                                        }
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                                        <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-slug="@question.Slug" class="btn btn-sm btn-gradient">
                                            <i class="fas fa-eye me-1"></i>View
                                        </a>
                                        <a asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@question.Id" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">
                                            <i class="fas fa-edit me-1"></i>Edit
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        }
    </div>

    <!-- Pagination -->
    @if (Model.TotalPages > 1)
    {
        <nav aria-label="My questions pagination" class="mt-4">
            <ul class="pagination justify-content-center">
                <li class="page-item @(Model.PageNumber == 1 ? "disabled" : "")">
                    <a class="page-link" asp-action="MyQuestions" asp-route-page="@(Model.PageNumber - 1)">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-left me-1"></i>Previous
                    </a>
                </li>
                
                @for (int i = Math.Max(1, Model.PageNumber - 2); i <= Math.Min(Model.TotalPages, Model.PageNumber + 2); i++)
                {
                    <li class="page-item @(i == Model.PageNumber ? "active" : "")">
                        <a class="page-link" asp-action="MyQuestions" asp-route-page="@i">
                            @i
                        </a>
                    </li>
                }
                
                <li class="page-item @(Model.PageNumber == Model.TotalPages ? "disabled" : "")">
                    <a class="page-link" asp-action="MyQuestions" asp-route-page="@(Model.PageNumber + 1)">
                        Next<i class="fas fa-chevron-right ms-1"></i>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    }
}

@section Scripts {
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    <script>
        function deleteQuestion(id, title) {
            Swal.fire({
                title: 'Delete Question?',
                html: `Are you sure you want to delete "<strong>${title}</strong>"?<br><small class="text-muted">This action cannot be undone.</small>`,
                icon: 'warning',
                showCancelButton: true,
                confirmButtonColor: '#dc3545',
                cancelButtonColor: '#6c757d',
                confirmButtonText: '<i class="fas fa-trash me-1"></i> Yes, Delete',
                cancelButtonText: '<i class="fas fa-times me-1"></i> Cancel',
                customClass: {
                    confirmButton: 'btn btn-danger',
                    cancelButton: 'btn btn-secondary'
                },
                buttonsStyling: false
            }).then((result) => {
                if (result.isConfirmed) {
                    $.ajax({
                        url: `/Questions/Delete/${id}`,
                        type: 'POST',
                        data: {
                            __RequestVerificationToken: $('input[name="__RequestVerificationToken"]').val()
                        },
                        success: function(response) {
                            if (response.success) {
                                Swal.fire({
                                    title: 'Deleted!',
                                    text: 'Your question has been deleted.',
                                    icon: 'success',
                                    timer: 2000,
                                    showConfirmButton: false
                                }).then(() => {
                                    location.reload();
                                });
                            } else {
                                Swal.fire('Error!', response.message || 'Failed to delete question', 'error');
                            }
                        },
                        error: function() {
                            Swal.fire('Error!', 'An error occurred while deleting the question', 'error');
                        }
                    });
                }
            });
        }

        // Add smooth animations
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.question-card');
            cards.forEach((card, index) => {
                card.style.opacity = '0';
                card.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    card.style.transition = 'all 0.5s ease';
                    card.style.opacity = '1';
                    card.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                }, index * 50);
            });
        });
    </script>
}
